<span class="headers">Oggok Beastlord (Scale) Armor</span>
<p>
<p>You say, 'i am beastlord'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Mez tink dat yuz were. Letz begin yur traineeng. Da furst ting dat yuz needz to do is gather da itemz dat will be uzed in da krafteeng of da armor and den yuz can kraft dem in dis majikal assembly kit.'</p>

<p>You say, 'what armor'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da itemz you will needz to gather will be all ober da Feerrott. Dese itemz will be hard for yuz to gather, dey come from some of da meanest tings in da Feerrott. Once yuz are redy to begin, tell mez da piece dat yuz wantz to kraft and mez will give yuz da recipez dat yuz will need when making da armor. I have recipez for [Caps], [Bracers], [Sleeves], [Boots], [Leggings], [Gloves] and [Tunics].'</p>

<p>You say, 'what caps'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Always gud to protekt yur nogginz, To kraft da cap, yuz needz to gather one yellow lizard scale, one piece of dark colored fungus, two pristine spider silks an combine dem in yur assembly kit. Once yuz got da material, yuz can take it to a loom and weave dem together with dis pattern to craft a cap to protekt yur hed.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Helm of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: HEAD <br>
AC: 3<br>
WIS: +1 HP: +5<br> 
WT: 2.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR </blockquote> </p>

<p>You say, 'what bracers'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da bracer is one o' da best itemz dat you can kraft, it protekts yur wrists from da harsh blows dey normally get fightin in da Feerrott. If yuz want to want to kraft a bracer, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, two bone chips, and one piece of light colored fungus, den yuz combine dem in yur magikal assembly kit to create da material yuz needz. Once yuz have da material, den you take it to a loom wit dis pattern and create yur bracer.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Bracer of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: WRIST <br>
AC: 2<br>
WIS: +1 HP: +4 <br>
WT: 1.0 Size: SMALL<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR</blockquote> </p>

<p>You say, 'what sleeves'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da sleeves is gud to get, yuz can never be too protektive of yur body, and da armz is whut you needz to do all yur huntin. If yuz want to kraft a sleeves, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, a long lizard tail, and one large snake skin, den yuz combine dem together in yur magikal assembly kit to create da material yuz needz. Once yuz have da material, den you take it to a loom wit dis pattern and create yur sleeves.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Armplates of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: ARMS <br>
AC: 3<br>
WIS: +2 HP: +4<br> 
WT: 2.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR </blockquote> </p>

<p>You say, 'what boots'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da bootz is someting dat you needz to wear often, specially when in da Feerrott, yuz never know when yuz might step in a surprize dat one o' da lizzies in dere might leeve for yuz. If yuz want to kraft a boots, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, a ruined wolf pelt, and two black spider silks, den yuz combine dem together in yur magikal assembly kit to create da material yuz needz. Once yuz have da material, den you take it to a loom wit dis pattern and create yur boots.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Boots of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: FEET <br>
AC: 3<br>
STR: +1 WIS: +1 MANA: +5 <br>
WT: 2.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR </blockquote></p>

<p>You say, 'what leggings'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da leggingz is almost da most impotent item dat you can kraft, and dey offer much protekshun. If yuz want to kraft a leggings, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, one long lizard tail, and two pristine lizard talons, den yuz combine dem together in yur magikal assembly kit to create da material yuz needz. Once yuz have da material, den you take it to a loom wit dis pattern and create yur leggingz.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Legplates of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: LEGS <br>
AC: 4<br>
WIS: +2 MANA: +10 <br>
WT: 2.0 Size: LARGE<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR </blockquote></p>

<p>You say, 'what gloves'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da glovez is also someting dat you want to get as soon as yuz can. Da fingerz is whut we use to keep us alive, witout dem, wez wud be in truble. If yuz want to kraft a gloves, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, two spiderling silks, and two pristine lizard talons, den yuz combine dem together in yur magikal assembly kit to create da material yuz needz. Once yuz have da material, den you take it to a loom wit dis pattern and create yur gloves.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Gauntlets of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: HANDS <br>
AC: 3<br>
WIS: +1 HP: +7 <br>
WT: 1.0 Size: SMALL<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR</blockquote></p>

<p>You say, 'what tunics'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'Da tunic is a gud piece to have, it protektz yuz from all da beatingz dat you get if you fight in da Feerrott. If yuz want to kraft a tunic, yuz need to gather one yellow lizard scale, two pristine lizard scales, one long lizard tail, and two black spider silks, and kraft dem into dis here majikal assembly kit to get yur tunic material. Den yuz take dat material to a loom wit dis pattern to make da tunic. After you make da armor, I have sumting else for you if you tink you [strong] enuff.'</p>

<p><blockquote>Initiate's Breastplate of the Scale<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Slot: CHEST <br>
AC: 8<br>
WIS: +3 HP: +7 MANA: +7 <br>
WT: 2.0 Size: LARGE<br>
Class: BST <br>
Race: OGR </blockquote></p>

<p>You say, 'i be strong'</p>

<p>Bakrishal says 'In da jungle dere be many dangerus beasts. You show you strong. You show you have power. Find da tree snakes and bring me four of dere fangs. You do this and I reward you.'</p>

<hr>

<p>SHOPPING LIST:</p>

<p>7 yellow lizard scale<br>
2 pristine lizard scales<br>
1 piece of dark colored fungus<br>
1 piece of light colored fungus<br>
2 pristine spider silks<br>
2 bone chips<br>
3 a long lizard tail<br>
1 large snake skin<br>
1 a ruined wolf pelt<br>
4 black spider silks<br>
4 pristine lizard talons<br>
2 spiderling silks</p>

<p>Quick recipes:</p>

<p>cap<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
1 piece of dark colored fungus<br>
2 pristine spider silks</p>

<p>bracer<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
2 bone chips<br>
1 piece of light colored fungus</p>

<p>sleeves<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
1 a long lizard tail<br>
1 large snake skin</p>

<p>boots<br>
one yellow lizard scale<br>
1 a ruined wolf pelt<br>
2 black spider silks</p>

<p>leggings<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
1 long lizard tail<br>
2 pristine lizard talons</p>

<p>gloves<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
2 spiderling silks<br>
2 pristine lizard talons</p>

<p>tunic<br>
1 yellow lizard scale<br>
2 pristine lizard scales<br>
1 long lizard tail<br>
2 black spider silks</p>

<p>weapon<br>
4 tree snake fang</p></p><p>
